The paper proposes an automated method for optimizing deep learning architectures through evolution, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the results of the method in object recognition and language modeling, which are subfields of machine learning (cs.LG). The method is applied to image captioning, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions the use of hyperparameters, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses language modeling, which is a subfield of natural language processing (cs.CL).
